|Aug humidity = 32\n|Sep humidity = 34\n|Oct humidity = 37\n|Nov humidity = 48\n|Dec humidity = 60\n|year humidity = 46\n|Jan sun = 212.6\n|Feb sun = 223.9\n|Mar sun = 239.1\n|Apr sun = 263.5\n|May sun = 310.8\n|Jun sun = 349.1\n|Jul sun = 334.7\n|Aug sun = 323.5\n|Sep sun = 325.2\n|Oct sun = 297.5\n|Nov sun = 253.0\n|Dec sun = 214.2\n|year sun = 3347.0\n|source=Fars province Meteorological Organization<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.farsmet.ir/DM/Files/files/jahrom.pdf |title=Jahrom |last= |first= |date= |website=Fars province Meteorological Organization |publisher= |access-date=2020-04-08 |quote=}}</ref>\n|accessdate=}}\n\n==Demographics==\n===Population===\n{{Population pyramid\n|year=2010\n|m0=3.7 |m5=3.4 |m10=3.6 |m15=4.3 |m20=6.0 |m25=6.4 |m30=4.5 |m35=3.4 |m40=3.3 |m45=3.0 |m50=2.6 |m55=2.1 |m60=1.3 |m65=1.0 |m70=0.7 |m75=0.6 |m80=0.4 |m85=0.4 \n|f0=3.5 |f5=3.2 |f10=3.5 |f15=4.0 |f20=5.8 |f25=6.1 |f30=4.7 |f35=3.5 |f40=3.3 |f45=2.9 |f50=2.4 |f55=1.9 |f60=1.3 |f65=1.0 |f70=0.7 |f75=0.6 |f80=0.4 |f85=0.4 \n|mmax=6.4\n|fmax=6.1\n}}\n{{As of|2016}}, Jahrom has a population of 141,634. Jahrom is the biggest city in the southern half of [[Fars Province]], the third one in whole province and 67th biggest city of [[Iran]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.citypopulation.de/Iran.html|title=Iran \u2013 City Population \u2013 Cities, Towns & Provinces \u2013 Statistics & Map|publisher=Citypopulation.de|date=3 November 2010|accessdate=5 May 2011}}</ref>\n[[File:JAHROM Population Change-ENG.jpg|thumb|left|230px|Jahrom population change]]\n{{Historical populations|1966|39354|1976|50333|1986|83478|1991|96690|1996|103627|2006|116562|2011|127159|2016|141634|align=center}}\n\n===Ethnics===\nThe main ethnic group in Jahrom constitutes of [[Persian people|Persians]], while  [[Basseri]]es and [[Iranian Arabs|Arabs]] constitute small minorities. They had nomadic life and later [[sedentism]].<ref>P. Oberling, \"F\u0100RS vii. Ethnography\", Encyclopaedia Iranica>{{cite web|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/fars-vii|title=F\u0100RS vii. Ethnography|date=31 May 2014}}</ref> Due to the geographical characteristics of Jahrom, specially good Rangeland for nomads, Jahrom has long been a residing area for these nomadic peoples.\n\n===Religion===\nThe majority of city are [[Shia Islam|Shia Muslims]], but there is also a small Immigrant [[Sunni Islam|Sunni]] minority in the city.<ref>Persian wikipedia</ref>\n\n==Economic==\n[[File:Nirugahe jahrom.jpg|250px|thumb|right|Jahrom combined cycle power plant]]\nJahrom's economic is based on agriculture. there are 350,000 [[Arecaceae|palm trees]] and 5.3 million [[citrus]] trees in Jahrom which makes Jahrom an agricultural pole in [[Iran]]. Jahrom produces %1.2 of the world's dates and %6 percent of its citrus fruits every year.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.irna.ir/news/80543857/%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%B1%D9%85-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%87-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%8A-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D9%86%DA%AF%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA |title= citrus of Jahrom |last= |first= |date= |website=Islamic Republic News Agency (IRNA) |publisher= |access-date=2020-04-08 |quote=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mehrnews.com/news/3864142/%D8%AC%D9%86%DA%AF%D9%84-%D9%86%D8%AE%D9%84-%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%88%D8%AF%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D8%B4%D9%87-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%B4%D9%87-%D9%86%D8%AE%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%B1%D9%85 |title=dates of Jahrom |last= |first= |date= |website=Mehr news |publisher= |access-date=2020-04-08 |quote=}}</ref>\n\nJahrom also has several factories including flour, dairy, brick, rug, plaster, plastic, jam, lemon juice, macaroni and cake factory.<ref>Persian wikipedia</ref>\n\n===Infrastructures===\n*Jahrom combined cycle power plant\n*Jahrom Petrochemistry\n*Jahrom especial economic zone\n*Jahrom economic town\n*Kosar economic town<ref>http://www.idro.ir/fa-ir/ActivityScopes/EconomicZones/Pages/Jahrom.aspx</ref>\n\n==Education==\n[[File:\u062f\u0627\u0646\u0634\u06af\u0627\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u0648\u0645 \u067e\u0632\u0634\u06a9\u06cc \u062c\u0647\u0631\u0645.jpg|250px|thumb|[[Jahrom University of Medical Sciences]], medical school]]\n===Colleges and universities===\nuniversities in city include:\n*[[Jahrom university]]\n*[[Jahrom University of Medical Sciences]] \n*[[Islamic Azad University, Jahrom Branch]]\n*[[Payame Noor university of Jahrom]]\n*Andisheh University\n*University of Applied Science and Technology Agriculture branch\n\n==Health==\n[[File:Jahrom motahari hospital.jpg|250px|thumb|Motahari hospital]]\n===Hospitals===\n*Peymanieh hospital\n*Motahhari hospital\n*Seyyedoshshohada hospital\n*Aboutalebi heart hospital<ref>[https://www.worldi.ir/7126 Hospitals of Fars province]</ref>\n\n===Medical centers===\n* Khatam ol-Anbia Cancer center\n* Javad ol-Aemeh Chemotherapy center\n* Honari Infertility Center\n* Hakim Salman Infertility Center\n* Honari speciality clinic\n* Emam Reza speciality clinic\n* Dental speciality clinic\n\n==Transport and communications==\n===Communication roads===\nThe most important roads in Jahrom are:\n*Jahrom-Shiraz highway \n*Jahrom-Lar under construction highway\n*Jahrom-Fasa road\n*Jahrom-Qir road\n*Jahrom-Khavaran-Sarvestan road\n*Jahrom-Hakan road\n*Jahrom-Simakan-Meymand road<ref>[http://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/1974617/%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C-%DB%B8-%DA%A9%DB%8C%D9%84%D9%88%D9%85%D8%AA%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%A8%D8%B2%D8%B1%DA%AF%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%87-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%B1%D9%85-%D8%B4%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B2 IRIB news]</ref><ref>[http://www.irna.ir/fars/fa/News/82892807 IRNA]</ref>\n\n===Airport===\n[[File:Jahrom Airport.jpg|thumb|220px|[[Jahrom Airport]]]]\n[[Jahrom Airport]], established in 1969, has weekly flights to Tehran [[Mehrabad Airport]] and [[Mashhad Airport]].<ref>[https://www.yjc.ir/fa/news/6535132/%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AA%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%B1%D9%85-%D9%88-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3 Tehran-Jahrom flights]</ref>\n\n===Railway===\nThere is an under construction railway project Connecting Shiraz to Bandar abbas which will have a station in Jahrom.<ref>[http://mldl.ir/?p=42335 Milad Larestan magazine]</ref>\n\n===Bus terminal===\nShahid Rahmanian is the bus terminal of Jahrom with daily buses to Shiraz, Tehran, Bandar abbas, Lar, etc.\n\n{{wide image|\u063a\u0627\u0631 \u0633\u0646\u06af \u062a\u0631\u0627\u0634\u0627\u0646.jpg|800px|A panorama of Jahrom near [[Sangtarashan cave]]}}\n\n==Notable Jahromis==\n* [[Barbad]], one of the first musicians in the world\n*[[Mohammad-Javad Azari Jahromi]], Iranian [[Ministry of Information and Communications Technology of Iran|Minister of Information and Communications Technology]]\n*[[Mohammad Jahromi]], former Iranian [[Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs (Iran)|minister of labour and social affairs]]\n*[[Ali Mohammad Besharati]], former Iranian [[Ministry of Interior (Iran)|Minister of Interior ]]\n*[[Mehdi Shabzendedar Jahromi]], Iranian\u00a0[[Shia]]\u00a0jurist and member of the\u00a0[[Guardian Council]]\n*[[Seyyed Hossein ayatollahi]], Shiite clergyman and\u00a0Ruhollah Khomeini's\u00a0Representative in\u00a0jahrom. \n*[[Abd al-Husayn Lari]], clergymen and jurists of South Iran\n*Lotfollah Dezhkam,\u00a0Ayatollah,\u00a0Friday leading prayer\u00a0of [[Shiraz]] and Representative of [[Guardianship of the Islamic Jurist|Guardian of the Islamic Jurist]] in [[Fars province]]\n*Mohammadreza Rezaei Kouchi, Representative of [[Iranian parliament]] and head of the civil commission of the parliament\n*Mirza Nasir Jahromi, Iranian architect and poet\n*Jahan, Persian singer\n*Sadroddin Zahed, Iranian director, actor and translator\n*[[Ali-Mohammad Khademi]], former general manager of\u00a0[[Iran Air]]\n*[[Ali Torab Jahromi]], Iranian poet\n\n== Gallery ==\n<gallery mode=packed 